dataset.title: A New Genus of Rhysipoline Wasp (Hymenoptera: Braconidae) with Modified Wing Venation from Africa and Papua New Guinea, Parasitoid on Choreutidae (Lepidoptera)

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Donald L. J. Quicke, Sergey A. Belokobylskij, M. Alex Smith (2016): A New Genus of Rhysipoline Wasp (Hymenoptera: Braconidae) with Modified Wing Venation from Africa and Papua New Guinea, Parasitoid on Choreutidae (Lepidoptera). Annales Zoologici 66 (2): 173-192, DOI: 10.3161/00034541Anz2016.66.2.003
